entry.title: Russia Resumes Strikes After Mass Bombardment of Ukraine
entry.content: Russia launched another round of strikes across Ukraine, many of which Kyiv said it intercepted, as the death toll rose from the previous day’s barrage, one of Moscow’s broadest assaults in nearly eight months of war.

entry.title: Smithsonian, Museums Return Stolen Benin Bronzes to Nigeria
entry.content: Some museums are returning pieces of art and antiquities countries say were taken unethically during colonization.
